{td}Hardware{/td}
{td}SN-3002-TR-ECTHNPKPH-N01 (RS-485 Modbus RTU, 7-in-1 soil), SHT10 (air temp/humidity, 2-wire serial), NDIR (CO2, UART); Valve, Heater, Fans, Humidifier; 4G Modem{/td}
{td}Physical sensing and actuation; irrigation, heating, ventilation, humidity{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}Edge Controller{/td}
{td}Arduino Portenta MC; STM32H747 Cortex-M7 (PID 10Hz) + Cortex-M4 (Local LAN MQTT); NV config storage{/td}
{td}Local PID/hysteresis automation; schedule execution; Local LAN MQTT publish{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
