{table class="wrapped"}
{colgroup}
 {col }
 {col }
 {col }
 {/colgroup}
{tr}
{th}**Interface**{/th}
{th}**Description / Scope**{/th}
{th}**Connected Component**{/th}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**SENS-HW-IF**{/td}
{td}Hardware interface to physical sensors: RS-485 Modbus RTU (SN-3002-TR-ECTHNPKPH-N01 soil probe), 2-wire Serial (SHT10 air sensor), UART/Modbus RTU (NDIR CO2 sensor). Driven by STM32H747 peripheral controllers. Not exposed beyond edge controller.{/td}
{td}Physical Sensors (Hardware Layer){/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**SENS-ENGINE-IF**{/td}
{td}Delivers SensorData events (parameter, value, unit, ISO 8601 timestamp, sensorId) and AlertEvent objects to Local Automation Engine. Triggered each polling cycle and immediately on threshold breach.{/td}
{td}Local Automation Engine{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**SENS-MQTT-IF**{/td}
{td}Serialises SensorData to JSON MQTT payloads (sensorId, parameter, value, unit, ISO 8601 timestamp). Passed to MQTT Client (Cortex-M4) for local publication to Mini PC at 60 s intervals.{/td}
{td}Local MQTT Broker (Mini PC){/td}
{/tr}
{/table}

