=== Local Automation Engine

{table class="wrapped"}
{colgroup}
 {col }
 {col }
 {/colgroup}
{tr}
{td}**Architectural Element**{/td}
{td}Local Automation Engine{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Component Type**{/td}
{td}Control Subsystem{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Responsible**{/td}
{td}Alexei Maxim{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Platform**{/td}
{td}STM32H747 Cortex-M7 Core; PID control (+/-0.5C setpoint stability); hysteresis for humidity; 10 Hz control cycle; EEPROM/Flash for NV config{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Purpose**{/td}
{td}Orchestrates all on-device automated greenhouse control. Receives sensor events, applies PID/hysteresis logic, issues actuator commands, executes scheduled irrigation, handles remote manual commands, and maintains local safety interlocks.{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Scope**{/td}
{td}Irrigation control (sensor/schedule/manual-triggered), climate PID/hysteresis, actuator conflict arbitration, threshold config persistence, resource usage logging, emergency stop enforcement{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Key Features**{/td}
{td}{ul}

- PID temperature control (+/-0.5C stability); hysteresis-based humidity control
- Irrigation valve activation within 30 s of soil moisture breach (SR-2.1); auto-stop within 30 s of reaching target regardless of trigger source (SR-2.2)
- Skip-if-wet gate: skips scheduled irrigation if soil already at/above target, preventing over-watering
- Maximum duration timer safeguard on pump prevents indefinite operation on sensor failure
- Autonomous schedule execution (daily/weekly) persisted in NV; survives restarts and WAN outages (SR-2.3)
- Remote manual irrigation commands from dashboard execute within 10 s (SR-2.4)
- Ventilation arbitration: temp and humidity breaches share physical actuator; each event logged independently with trigger type
- ResourceLogger: records water volume, energy, trigger type (SENSOR|SCHEDULE|MANUAL), timestamp per activation event (SR-7.3)
- ActuatorSafetyInterlock: emergency stop reachable from any state; all actuators to safe state within 60 s
{/ul}{/td}
{/tr}
{/table}

==== {image file="local_automation_engine_component.png" width=749}

==== Component Interfaces

{table class="wrapped"}
{colgroup}
 {col }
 {col }
 {col }
 {/colgroup}
{tr}
{th}**Interface**{/th}
{th}**Description / Scope**{/th}
