{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**AUTO-SENS-IF**{/td}
{td}Receives SensorData and AlertEvent from Sensor Acquisition System. Entry point to AutomationDecisionEngine. Driven by 60 s polling cycle.{/td}
{td}Sensor Acquisition System{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**AUTO-ACT-IF**{/td}
{td}Issues GPIO/relay actuation commands to physical actuators (valve, heater, exhaust/circ fan, humidifier). SLA: 30 s automated, 10 s manual remote.{/td}
{td}Physical Actuators (Hardware Layer){/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**AUTO-API-IF**{/td}
{td}Receives manual remote control commands from Mini PC Edge Gateway via MQTT downlink. Executes within 10 s of dashboard submission. Guarded by EdgeAuthModule in offline mode.{/td}
{td}Mini PC Edge Gateway{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**AUTO-CONFIG-IF**{/td}
{td}Reads and writes threshold configuration (4 parameters) from ThresholdConfigStore (NV). Persists across restarts; applies immediately; syncs from cloud within 60 s cycle (SR-2.6).{/td}
{td}ThresholdConfigStore (NV Storage){/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**AUTO-SCHED-IF**{/td}
{td}Retrieves and persists irrigation schedules from ScheduleExecutor. Schedules survive cloud outages and controller restarts (SR-2.3).{/td}
{td}ScheduleExecutor{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**AUTO-LOG-IF**{/td}
{td}Passes resource usage records (water volume, energy, trigger type, timestamp) to Cloud Time-Series DB for 90-day retention (SR-7.3).{/td}
{td}Cloud Time-Series DB (via MQTT pipeline){/td}
{/tr}
{/table}

