=== Cloud Backend System

{table class="wrapped"}
{colgroup}
 {col }
 {col }
 {/colgroup}
{tr}
{td}**Architectural Element**{/td}
{td}Cloud Backend System{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Component Type**{/td}
{td}Cloud Backend Subsystem{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Responsible**{/td}
{td}Raeeva Daria{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Platform**{/td}
{td}MQTT Broker (Mosquitto/EMQX); InfluxDB or TimescaleDB; REST API (HTTPS); AuthN/AuthZ (JWT+RBAC); Notification gateway (Twilio/FCM){/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Purpose**{/td}
{td}Receives telemetry via MQTT/TLS, persists sensor readings 90 days, evaluates alerts, dispatches push/SMS notifications, serves HTTPS REST API to dashboard, enforces RBAC, provides analytics and export.{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Scope**{/td}
{td}MQTT broker with X.509 mTLS, data ingestion, InfluxDB/TimescaleDB 90-day store, alert evaluation, two-tier notification dispatch, REST API with RBAC, analytics, resource usage storage, notification gateway, AI Agent Service{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Key Features**{/td}
{td}{ul}

- MQTT broker accepts connections only with valid X.509 certs; TLS 1.2+ and QoS 1 to prevent data loss on 4G/5G (SR-9.1)
- Data ingestion handles normal 30-60 s telemetry and batch historical sync on edge reconnect
- InfluxDB/TimescaleDB 90-day retention; ISO 8601 timestamps and sensor IDs on all records (SR-5.1)
- In-dashboard alert generation 5 s from breach; yellow=warning, red=critical (SR-4.1)
- Critical alert escalation: push/SMS within 30 s of 60 s persistence; SLA at server dispatch point (SR-4.2, review R5)
- Heat Warning / Frost Warning temperature alert categorisation (SR-4.4)
- Interactive trend queries up to 90 days; daily render 3 s, hourly 5 s (SR-5.2)
- CSV and XLSX export with 5 mandatory fields: timestamp, sensor ID, parameter, value, unit (SR-5.3)
- Setpoint/config updates acknowledged by edge within one 60 s control cycle (SR-2.6)
- Multi-site aggregation: 10 sites, initial load 5 s, refresh 3 s (SR-8.3, SR-8.5)
- REST API returns HTTP 401/403 for unauthenticated/unauthorised requests; logs with timestamp and source IP (SR-9.3)
- AI Agent Service operates as an API client to suggest optimized setpoints based on 90-day historical trends.
{/ul}{/td}
{/tr}
{/table}

