{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**CLOUD-NOTIF-IF**{/td}
{td}Interface to Twilio/FCM push/SMS gateway. Triggered when critical alert persists beyond 60 s; notification enqueued within 30 s (SR-4.2). Includes Heat/Frost Warning label in payload.{/td}
{td}External Push/SMS Provider{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**CLOUD-DB-IF**{/td}
{td}Internal: DataIngestionService to InfluxDB/TimescaleDB. Writes all sensor readings and resource logs; enforces 90-day retention; serves queries for dashboard and export.{/td}
