{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**CLOUD-AUTH-IF**{/td}
{td}Internal: REST API Gateway to AuthNAuthZService. Validates JWT tokens, enforces Operator/Viewer roles, logs all unauthorised attempts with timestamp and source IP.{/td}
{td}AuthNAuthZService{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**CLOUD-SYNC-IF**{/td}
{td}Receives batch-flushed buffered records from reconnecting edge controllers. Inserts chronologically into DB with zero data loss (SR-6.2).{/td}
{td}Mini PC Offline Buffer (on reconnect){/td}
