=== Web Dashboard & User Interface System

{table class="wrapped"}
{colgroup}
 {col }
 {col }
 {/colgroup}
{tr}
{td}**Architectural Element**{/td}
{td}Web Dashboard & User Interface System{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Component Type**{/td}
{td}Presentation Subsystem{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Responsible**{/td}
{td}Mutruc Victoria{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Platform**{/td}
{td}Browser SPA (no install); HTTPS/REST; WebSocket or SSE; Chrome >=110, Firefox >=110, Safari >=16, Edge >=110{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Purpose**{/td}
{td}Operator-facing SPA for real-time greenhouse monitoring, manual control, alert management, historical data access, threshold and schedule configuration, resource analysis, and multi-site overview. Accessible from any modern browser, 360 px viewport upward.{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Scope**{/td}
{td}Responsive SPA 360-2560 px; live sensor dashboard (soil moisture primary); colour-coded alert panel; irrigation control (manual ON/OFF, Operator role gated); schedule manager; threshold config UI; historical trend view + export; resource summary + baseline; multi-site aggregated dashboard; side-by-side cross-site comparison{/td}
{/tr}
{tr}
{td}**Key Features**{/td}
{td}{ul}

- Single-page overview: all sensor values, alerts, and actuator statuses without navigation (SR-3.2)
- Soil moisture primary top-viewport widget visible without scrolling at 360 px (SR-2.5)
- Auto-refresh 10 s without manual reload (SR-3.4); freshness timestamp always visible; staleness warning when data >60 s (SR-3.6)
- Fully responsive 360-2560 px; touch targets >=44 px; no horizontal overflow at 360 px (SR-3.3)
- Complete feature parity desktop/mobile: every control reachable on smartphone (SR-3.5)
- Colour-coded alert banners within 5 s of breach; Heat/Frost Warning type labels (SR-4.1, SR-4.4)
- Manual irrigation ON/OFF with 10 s SLA; requires Operator role (SR-2.4)
- Historical trend: 90 days, hourly/daily granularity; CSV and XLSX export with 5 mandatory fields (SR-5.2, SR-5.3)
- Resource summary panel: water + energy for selected period vs. manually-entered baseline with % difference (SR-7.4)
- Multi-site dashboard: 10 sites, initial load 5 s, auto-refresh 3 s over 4G/5G (SR-8.3, SR-8.5)
- Side-by-side parameter comparison; colour-coded out-of-range highlight (SR-8.4)
{/ul}{/td}
{/tr}
{/table}

